299
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:38,900
I'm fine.

300
00:15:56,280 --> 00:15:57,330
Shen Jiahe.

301
00:15:59,200 --> 00:15:59,730
Shen Jiahe.

302
00:15:59,750 --> 00:16:01,570
Why didn't you answer the phone?

303
00:16:02,590 --> 00:16:04,020
I couldn't find you.

304
00:16:15,830 --> 00:16:16,450
Nuo.

305
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:18,450
You really love me.

306
00:16:34,110 --> 00:16:34,730
Why aren't you dressed

307
00:16:34,750 --> 00:16:36,380
in broad daylight?

308
00:16:39,750 --> 00:16:40,940
Because I'm taking a bath.

309
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,660
What are you doing here so early?

310
00:16:52,510 --> 00:16:53,610
Good girl. Wait for me for a while.

311
00:16:56,110 --> 00:16:56,490
By the way,

312
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:58,260
since you're in Beijiang

313
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,300
and not in a hurry to go back,

314
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:00,490
see where you want to go.

315
00:17:14,360 --> 00:17:15,730
Xu Nuo.

316
00:17:16,310 --> 00:17:17,010
Didn't you come to ask him

317
00:17:17,030 --> 00:17:18,290
when he's going back?

318
00:17:26,600 --> 00:17:27,180
Mr. Shen.

319
00:17:27,470 --> 00:17:28,820
[Publicist, Wan Shu]
Yuan Fei's president

320
00:17:28,840 --> 00:17:30,250
