321
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,820
If this is okay,

322
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:33,180
we'll upload it to Yuan Fei's Public account.

323
00:17:35,030 --> 00:17:35,660
Not yet.

324
00:17:35,840 --> 00:17:36,490
Hold on.

325
00:17:40,270 --> 00:17:41,770
6:10.

326
00:17:48,420 --> 00:17:51,300
[6:10 p.m.]

327
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:12,660
That's what you said

328
00:18:14,030 --> 00:18:15,050
about not being able to reply to me

329
00:18:15,120 --> 00:18:16,610
because of the water damage to your phone, right?

330
00:18:24,610 --> 00:18:29,960
♪I love you, love you, love you♪

331
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:38,930
♪'Til I forget who I am♪

